\lim_{(x,y)\rightarrow (0,0)} \frac{x^2y^2}{x^3+y^3} = \lim_{x\rightarrow 0} \frac{x^2. (x^4-x^3)^{\frac{2}{3}}}{x^3+x^4-x^3}
